      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a comprehensive online platform for ProjectHubX, an academic and real-world project center and service business. The platform will facilitate the sale of ready-made projects, manage custom project development, handle client and developer interactions, and automate project delivery and payments."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Homepage Content**: Displays brand information, animated counters, featured projects carousel, 'how it works' section, testimonials, and CTA buttons.\n- **View Project Listing**: Shows ready-made projects categorized and filterable by various criteria.\n- **View Project Details**: Provides detailed information for individual ready-made projects, including description, features, tech stack, screenshots, demo video, and deliverables.\n- **Submit Custom Project Request**: Allows users to submit detailed, multi-step forms for custom project development.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Enables visitors to send inquiries to the business.\n- **User Authentication**: Supports email/password login, Google OAuth, OTP verification, and role-based access (Admin, Developer, Client).\n- **View Client Dashboard**: Allows clients to view purchased projects, download files, track progress, use chat, manage support tickets, submit revision requests, view payment history, and access version control.\n- **View Admin Dashboard**: Enables administrators to manage projects (CRUD), orders, clients, and developers, assign projects, view analytics, manage coupons, generate invoices, send notifications, and control file access.\n- **View Developer Dashboard**: Allows developers to see assigned projects, upload deliverables, chat with clients, update status, and track deadlines.\n- **AI Chatbot**: Provides automated assistance and answers to user queries.\n- **Process Payments**: Handles secure online payments, including partial and milestone payments, with auto-invoicing and refund management.\n- **Automated File Delivery**: Manages secure cloud storage for project files with time-limited links, role-based access, versioned uploads, and DRM protection.",
